<section>
<h2>Data Source and Methodology</h2>
<p>All calculations are based on the most recent data available from the California Department of Tax and Fee Administration. <a href="https://www.cdtfa.ca.gov" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Visit their website for more details.</a> All calculations are strictly based on the formulas and data provided by this source.</p>
